OL,3,COffenders to be released early as
OL,4,Cprison system faces 'collapse', says
OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,FIn an announcement on Friday, Justice
OL,8,FSecretary Shabana Mahmood warned of a
OL,9,F"total breakdown of law and order"
OL,10,Funless the government took immediate
OL,11,Faction to address the overcrowding
OL,12,Fcrisis in jails.
OL,14,FMahmood said prisons were "on the
OL,15,Fpoint of collapse", with barely 700
OL,16,Fplaces left in the adult male estate
OL,17,Fand jails operating at 99% capacity
OL,18,Fsince the start of 2023.
