OL,3,COffenders to be released early as
OL,4,Cprison system faces 'collapse', says
OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,FIf prisons ran out of cell space, she
OL,8,Fwarned the country faced the prospect
OL,9,Fof "van-loads of dangerous people
OL,10,Fcircling the country with nowhere to
OL,11,Fgo".
OL,13,FThe plans set out by Mahmood will see
OL,14,Fa temporary reduction in the
OL,15,Fproportion of the sentence many
OL,16,Fprisoners must serve in jail from 50%
OL,17,Fto 40%.
OL,19,F"I fully understand there is risk
OL,20,Fattached with doing so', she said.
