OL,3,COffenders to be released early as
OL,4,Cprison system faces 'collapse', says
OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,FThe justice secretary made clear the
OL,8,Fplan would not apply to violent
OL,9,Foffenders serving more than four
OL,10,Fyears, sex offenders or those in
OL,11,Fprison for crimes connected to
OL,12,Fdomestic abuse. Dangerous offenders
OL,13,Fserving extended or life sentences
OL,14,Fwould also be exempted from the scheme.
OL,16,FMost prisoners currently serve 50% of
OL,17,Ftheir sentence in jail, with the
OL,18,Fremaining 50% being served on licence
OL,19,Fand under threat of being returned to
OL,20,Fprison if they break their parole
OL,21,Fconditions.
