OL,4,Cprison system faces 'collapse', says
OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,FMahmood stressed that "this is an
OL,8,Femergency measure" and "not a
OL,9,Fpermanent change", insisting "I am
OL,10,Funapologetic in my belief that
OL,11,Fcriminals must be punished."
OL,13,FThe justice secretary blamed the
OL,14,Fprevious government for the crisis in
OL,15,Fjails, saying they "left the country
OL,16,Fof the brink of disaster" and "courted
OL,17,Fcatastrophe".
