OL,4,Cprison system faces 'collapse', says
OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,FIt is expected to come into force in
OL,8,FSeptember, giving the Probation
OL,9,FService time to plan for offenders'
OL,10,Frelease.
OL,12,FThe Justice Secretary also announced
OL,13,Fthe recruitment of 1,000 additional
OL,14,Ftrainee probation officers by March
OL,15,Fand an end to the previous
OL,16,Fgovernment's early release scheme,
OL,17,Fwhich saw 10,000 prisoners released up
OL,18,Fto 70 days early.
