OL,7,FThe End of Custody Supervised License
OL,8,FScheme (ECSL) initially involved
OL,9,Finmates being released up to 18 days
OL,10,Fearly. That was then extended to
OL,11,Fbetween 35 and 60 days in March, and
OL,12,Ffurther extended to 70 days in May.
OL,14,FNew government figures released on
OL,15,FFriday show more than 10,000 prisoners
OL,16,Fwere released up to 70 days early
OL,17,Funder the scheme.
